<inglise> Programmes may be multiannual and must include the following information: </inglise>
<eesti> Programmid v&otilde;ivad olla mitmeaastased ja peavad sisaldama j&auml;rgmist teavet: </eesti>
<inglise> - description and analysis of the situation at the outset as regards inspectors and equipment, </inglise>
